Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠在一起 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}六月2日 Goinia
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,末路狂花華爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}劫持巡邏車繼續逃亡的Michiko Malandro嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}據推測此次的事故是其在警方的追擊之下失誤而落入河中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}被發現的巡邏車中并無尸體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在周邊區域的搜索仍在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}重復一遍 通緝中的Michiko Malandro嫌疑犯的行蹤仍然不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在警方正在盡全力搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要拖我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事嗎 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的老大是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Juninho 有客人 帶著"禮物"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"禮物"？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該吃多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成人是3粒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成倍的吃 就有成倍的藥效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在這里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那些家伙去找Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道他在哪里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經實現了諾言 請放了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你敢和我Satoshi Batista作對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到過長相相似的人 但是無法肯定就是這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能隨便亂說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什么地方見到的？ 和什么人在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人 看起來有點危險的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事找我的就是大叔你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這個家伙的老爸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi Morenos？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來沒有問過你叫什么名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok Satoru先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以聽我說兩句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也在找他 這個大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠了我一大筆錢就銷聲匿跡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也不想老是提錢的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要恨就恨你的朋友Hiroshi Morenos吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫是搞詐騙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 未來的大總統
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}确认是追捕中的嫌疑犯 马上逮捕她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是第一大街 發現通緝中的嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑犯沿著第一大街向集市的廣場移動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認持有手槍 請求緊急增援
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要錢的話就去把Hiroshi Morenos找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嚇的尿褲子的事情我會替你保密的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是的 是Michiko Malandro嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}剛才的槍擊事件肯定是Michiko Malandro嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在她正據守在集市廣場的移動游樂場里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Michiko Malandro嫌疑犯依然據守在集市廣場的游樂場里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}根據情報 她劫持了游樂場里的3名員工為人質
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}重復一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Michiko Malandro嫌疑犯依然據守在集市廣場的游樂場里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何？ Miguel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她持有武器 無法輕易接近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方只不過是一個女人 太失態了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛 是因為這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會對你們用的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑犯逃走 隊員擊中了人質 生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是嫌疑犯的槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 小心保管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您... 打算做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:13:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那個女人背黑鍋 然后忘記這件事情 Miguel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警視發來通知 說是要前來接管Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請抓活的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 Miguel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你一個人的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Michiko Malandro向人質開槍后逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}被害者在救治醫院因為失血過多死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}面對一般市民可以毫不猶豫地開槍的殘忍犯罪行為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我們的憤怒無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}附件的居民請務必小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是在騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什么告訴你地方就放了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又說什么到了地方就放了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖拖拉拉的搞什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！ 放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學學如何一個人生存下去的堅強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你一個人去就好了！ 你一點都不堅強！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里出亂子了？ 完全看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個死老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Juninho 那個人是Satoshi Batista
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的話 那個大叔一定非常值錢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到Hiroshi了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:16:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算逃走 你不去追嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 Michiko在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神佛都在向我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了 你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都可以給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Satoshi Batista
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:19:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們全都死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？ 你說什么？ 我聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你屎拉在褲子上的事情讓我提你保密？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列車即將出發
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要乘車的旅客請在站臺等候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Centro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
